description: It's a 1987 30 foot Valco with a 2008 Mercury 4 stroke 60 HP engine that runs like new. It has a full bathroom with a big shower and toilet that is not a porta potty, it has a holding tank for waste. Stove,Microwave, and refrigerator in the kitchen. It sleeps 4 inside and as many as you want up on the top deck. Generator and a inverter that runs everything. It has 3 pontoons so it is the most stable boat on the lake. When the waves hit the other boats they rock excessively but this boat doesn't feel the waves at all. I have it priced a little higher than the best homemade boat on the lake because this one is made so much better. The other boats have lots of corners cut when they were made but this is a manufacture boat and built to last. The boats with wood pontoons have to be taken out of the lake every 5 years or so and redone but these metal pontoons will last forever. I really don't want to sell my boat but I'm not using it as much as it deserves. So don't try to lowball me and do your research on the other boats on the lake. It also has a heater and ac unit so you can use it all year long. It has custom wood blinds through out and I reupholstered all the furniture inside. It looks like a cabin in the hills and is the most livable boat on Kaweah at this time. It is in the middle row which is the best one for fishing it's at sp#151. CASH ONLY No Emails,No Paypal,NO SCAMS! I don't want you to sell it for me. Don't waste my time with your scams.
